import math

def fun_carrylessadd(x, y):
  result=0
  multiplier=1
  digitsum=0
  while(x or y):
    digitsum=((x%10)+(y%10))
    digitsum=digitsum%10
    result=(digitsum*multiplier)+result
    x=math.floor(x/10)
    y=math.floor(y/10)
    multiplier=multiplier*10
    
    
  return result
